column5: Havnt been up this early in a while.  Heading up to Nip today to fish with some fellow board members.  Hope the conditions are OK!
If I can get out of my driveway and dirt road, then we'll meet up haha.   It doesn't seem so early when you go to sleep at 830pm. Lew, what time do you crash-out? Right after desert?
Some days I don't last till desert LOL
Just passed Powwasan.    Making great time.
